window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Matteo Amante.</p> <p>Dangerous. Deadly. And most of all, devastating.&nbsp;</p> <p>He’s the king of the city. Running the Mafia and ruling the East Coast. He’s at war with his cousin, and I am the casualty.&nbsp;</p> <p>There is nothing Matteo won’t do to win.&nbsp;He’ll burn everything down to the ground, my hopes and dreams included.</p> <p>He’s no hero.&nbsp;He’s the handsome devil who will probably kill me in the end.&nbsp;</p> <p>Falling in love with the enemy can destroy me, especially when he is my husband....</p>"; 
